co.cask.coopr.runtime

Class MockProvisionerMain

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.coopr.common.daemon.DaemonMain
      • co.cask.coopr.runtime.MockProvisionerMain

  • public final class MockProvisionerMain
extends DaemonMain
    Mock provisioner. Will communicate with a server, registering, heartbeating, taking tasks, and spinning up and down tenant workers. However, the workers will not perform any actual work and will instead always return back a success.
